{"id":10817,"date":"2024-01-19T17:49:00","date_gmt":"2020-06-19T12:19:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=10817"},"modified":"2022-06-15T21:14:07","modified_gmt":"2022-06-15T15:44:07","slug":"vastu-colours-for-bedroom","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/vastu-colours-for-bedroom\/","title":{"rendered":"Ultimate Guide To Picking Your Bedroom Colour According to Vastu"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Start your day on the right note with these Vastu colours for your bedroom<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Vastu Shastra is ancient Indian wisdom that suggests the ideal design and layout for the home to ensure an optimal balance of energies for wellbeing and prosperity. Along with cardinal directions and placement of items within the house, Vastu Shashtra also prescribes colours that help one achieve their needs.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The recommendations are rooted in the belief that colours emit energies that influence our moods and temperament. Advice for choosing bedroom colour according to Vastu is sought after as this is where you begin and end each day. Vastu colors for the bedroom, depending on your personality and requirements, help to balance your emotions.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this blog you will find the right colour combination for your bedroom according to Vastu. It also includes the most recommended Vastu colors for the master bedroom. The Vastu tips for bedroom colour show you how to maximise the properties of these colours.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Vastu Shastra Bedroom Colour For New Couples<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Red is a highly recommended colour for the master bedroom particularly if you&#8217;re a new couple living together for the first time. It&#8217;s no surprise why! Red is the colour that universally represents love. Having this colour in the bedroom evokes feelings of warmth and intimacy. The idea of red walls is not as outlandish as you think. When balanced with shades of brown, the bedroom gets a tasteful facelift. Besides, shades of brown are also highly recommended as ideal colours for a master bedroom according to Vastu as it represents stability.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172804\/red-and-brown-vastu-colors-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Red universally represents love, and brown represents stability are colour combinations for the bedroom according to Vastu.\" class=\"wp-image-10822\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172804\/red-and-brown-vastu-colors-for-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172804\/red-and-brown-vastu-colors-for-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172804\/red-and-brown-vastu-colors-for-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172804\/red-and-brown-vastu-colors-for-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bedroom Colour According To Vastu That Stimulates Desire<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s not just new couples but couples that have been together for a long time can benefit from the energies of red in the bedroom as well. According to Vastu Shashtra, red is an active colour that works as a stimulant. So, those looking to reignite the passion can use the energies of red to fuel desires. If you think the colour is too bold for your bedroom walls, you can opt for red bedding and mellow the colour palette with the help of white and grey. Vastu colours for your bedroom are not limited to wall paint and can be incorporated in any way you like.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172902\/red-bedding-best-colour-for-bedroom-vastu.jpg\" alt=\"Vastu Shastra bedroom colour red bedding and mellow is an actual colour that works as a stimulant.\" class=\"wp-image-10823\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172902\/red-bedding-best-colour-for-bedroom-vastu.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172902\/red-bedding-best-colour-for-bedroom-vastu-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172902\/red-bedding-best-colour-for-bedroom-vastu-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172902\/red-bedding-best-colour-for-bedroom-vastu-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Do you believe that home interiors must be vastu compliant\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02170838\/home-interiors-must-be-vastu-compliant.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Vastu Colours For A Bedroom To Achieve Your Goals<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Like red, orange belongs to the family of colours that represents the fire element. This shade is all about action, energy and ambition. According to Vastu bedroom colour orange is ideal for young professionals who have just started out in their career. The energies of this shade boost determination towards achieving one&#8217;s goals. This colour bedroom is also recommended for people who tend to feel low often. According to the ancient wisdom of architecture, orange is an increasing colour and its energies help lift your mood. However, people who have a short temper should stay away from this colour that symbolises fire. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173235\/vastu-tips-for-bedroom-colour-orange.jpg\" alt=\"Orange Vastu colors for bedroom is all about action, energy and ambition vastu tips for bedroom colour\" class=\"wp-image-10827\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173235\/vastu-tips-for-bedroom-colour-orange.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173235\/vastu-tips-for-bedroom-colour-orange-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173235\/vastu-tips-for-bedroom-colour-orange-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173235\/vastu-tips-for-bedroom-colour-orange-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Most Recommended Master Bedroom Colours According To Vastu<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Brown is the best colour for bedroom according to Vastu, especially the master bedroom. The colour represents all things earthy like soil and the trunk of a tree. It stands for qualities of the earth such as stability, permanence, groundedness and reliability. So, introducing brown in your bedroom is a good way to ensure that these characteristics always find a place in your family. Instead of going for brown wall paint, installing plywood on the wall and flooring will be a trendier choice. Bedrooms situated in the southwest reap the maximum benefits of this colour as this direction is ruled by the earth element, according to the principles of Vastu.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172710\/brown-vastu-colors-for-master-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Brown Vastu colors for master bedroom instead of going for wall paint, installing plywood on the wall trendier choice.\" class=\"wp-image-10821\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172710\/brown-vastu-colors-for-master-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172710\/brown-vastu-colors-for-master-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172710\/brown-vastu-colors-for-master-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172710\/brown-vastu-colors-for-master-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also Read: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/master-bedroom-colour-ideas\/\">Best Master Bedroom Color Schemes For Your Home<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bedroom Colours To Suit Any Personality<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>White is another colour that ranks high in the recommendation list of Vastu colours for a bedroom. The energies of this colour, that globally symbolises peace, also represent qualities like purity, clarity, simplicity and intimacy. So pick white as your bedroom colour if you are looking to strengthen these values in your life. According to Vastu bedrooms with a white colour palette is said to be a fit for every type of personality and doesn&#8217;t have any negative effects. Since plain white walls can begin to feel boring, a textured finish does well to break the monotony. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173330\/white-vastu-paint-colors-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"White Vastu paint colors for bedroom represent qualities like purity, clarity, simplicity and intimacy.\" class=\"wp-image-10828\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173330\/white-vastu-paint-colors-for-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173330\/white-vastu-paint-colors-for-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173330\/white-vastu-paint-colors-for-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173330\/white-vastu-paint-colors-for-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Best Colour For Bedroom Vastu To Resolve Fights<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Instantly reminding one of the glories of nature, from lush trees to carpets of grass, it&#8217;s no wonder that the ancient wisdom of Vastu considers green to be a positive colour. According to Vastu bedroom colour green radiates positive energy and has an especially calming effect on people prone to irritability and stubbornness. Green is a highly recommended bedroom colour according to Vastu particularly for couples constantly at odds with each other. The healing properties of green effectively soothe flaring tempers and stabilise moods.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172632\/bedroom-colour-according-to-vastu-positive-green.jpg\" alt=\"Vastu tips for bedroom color green radiate effectively soothe flaring tempers and stabilise moods.\" class=\"wp-image-10820\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172632\/bedroom-colour-according-to-vastu-positive-green.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172632\/bedroom-colour-according-to-vastu-positive-green-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172632\/bedroom-colour-according-to-vastu-positive-green-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172632\/bedroom-colour-according-to-vastu-positive-green-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bedroom Colour According To Vastu For Prosperity<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The often-used phrase &#8216;nature&#8217;s bounty&#8217; is an apt representation of the feelings that nature evokes in us. Abundance and generosity characterise nature and these qualities are reflected by the colour green as well. This is the best colour for the bedroom according to Vastu if you&#8217;re seeking to invite abundance into your home. Green also represents the quality of growth in nature. This is why according to Vastu bedroom colour green invites prosperity and opportunities for growth into one&#8217;s life. The wall behind the headboard painted in bottle green instantly gives your bedroom a refined and elegant look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173137\/vastu-shastra-bedroom-colour-bottle-green.jpg\" alt=\"According to Vastu bedroom colour, bottle green representation of the feelings that nature evokes in us\" class=\"wp-image-10826\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173137\/vastu-shastra-bedroom-colour-bottle-green.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173137\/vastu-shastra-bedroom-colour-bottle-green-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173137\/vastu-shastra-bedroom-colour-bottle-green-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173137\/vastu-shastra-bedroom-colour-bottle-green-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Want vastu approved home interior design solutions\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15142702\/want-vastu-approved-home-interior-design-solutions.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Relax Easy With These Vastu Colors For Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The ideal colour combination for a bedroom according to Vastu is green and brown as it blends both colours that represent the earth. With this colour theme, all the energies associated with the attributes of the earth will be heightened. Pairing a green wall with plywood flooring gives the bedroom a graceful look. This combination enhances feelings of being closer to nature. Besides, the best colour for bedroom Vastu is green as the energies of this colour aid relaxation. So, if you find it difficult to unwind or get a good night&#8217;s sleep, green is the Vastu recommended colour for a bedroom colour you must consider.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173037\/vastu-colors-for-bedroom-green-and-brown.jpg\" alt=\"Colour combination for bedroom according to Vastu green and brown as it blends both colours that represent the earth.\" class=\"wp-image-10825\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173037\/vastu-colors-for-bedroom-green-and-brown.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173037\/vastu-colors-for-bedroom-green-and-brown-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173037\/vastu-colors-for-bedroom-green-and-brown-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19173037\/vastu-colors-for-bedroom-green-and-brown-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Best Colour For Bedroom Vastu To Promote Harmony<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Blue is yet another colour that makes you feel closer to nature. This colour symbolises water and brings to mind the calm seas and vastness of the sky. Using blue in the bedroom is believed to boost feelings of tranquillity and contentment. The energies of this colour are beneficial in enhancing happiness and harmony. According to Vastu a bedroom coloured in blue is most effective in the west as this direction is ruled by Varun, the god of water. While blue is a suitable colour for a bedroom according to Vastu, make sure you balance it with another colour like white. The ancient wisdom suggests that too much blue could lead to frequent cold and cough.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172527\/bedroom-colour-according-to-vastu-blue.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom wall colors according to Vastu While blue symbolises water and brings to mind the calm seas and vastness of the sky\" class=\"wp-image-10819\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172527\/bedroom-colour-according-to-vastu-blue.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172527\/bedroom-colour-according-to-vastu-blue-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172527\/bedroom-colour-according-to-vastu-blue-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/19172527\/bedroom-colour-according-to-vastu-blue-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Keep these Vastu tips for bedroom colour in mind the next time you plan to redecorate your bedroom. If you&#8217;re setting up a new home, these recommendations of Vastu colours for the master bedroom will make your decisions easier.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Read More:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/bedroom-colour-combinations\/\">A Guide To Bedroom Colour Combination&nbsp;<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/bedroom-paint-colours\/\">10 Best Bedroom Paint Colour Options<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/bl